name: TNT
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (1 oz)     Cognac
  - (1 oz)     Absinth
  - (1 oz)     Cointreau
  - (5 dashes) Angostura Bitters
  - (1 twist)  Lemon Rind

steps:
  - Shake cognac, absinth, and cointreau in shaker with ice
  - Strain into chilled glass and add bitters
  - Add lemon twist as garnish
